Roschdy Zem https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roschdy_Zem 0 Roschdy Zem (born 27 September 1965) is a French actor and filmmaker of Moroccan descent. He shared the award for Best Actor for his role in the film Days of Glory at the 2006 Cannes Film Festival.
